value:
The two took shelter in an old house...
An urge to clean took hold of them!

They found a diary and read from it...
Hardly any cleaning got done at all!

They focused on cleaning until sunup!
Satisfied, they continued on the road!

They returned the house to its glory!
Even the floors shone and sparkled!

A statue of Feh atop a seashell that radiates
a summery aura. It depicts Feh rising from the
sea and exudes a sense of love and beauty.

Used in Aether Raids to build structures that
are available for a limited time. If that period
has elapsed, these stones will be lost.
